headline: Seagate Elevates HDD Performance Through Aerial Density Advancements
summary: STX's areal density roadmap and HAMR-powered Mozaic drives keep HDDs cost-efficient as hyperscalers scale AI storage to 36TB and beyond.

headline: As AI Breaks the One-Size-Fits-All Data Stack, Yuki Raises $6M to Become the AI Data Control Layer
summary: Yuki, a data cost optimization startup, has emerged from stealth with a $6 million seed round led by Hyperwise Ventures, with participation from VelocitX, Tal Ventures, Fresh.fund, and Yakir Daniel, founder of Spot.io (Flexera).

headline: NetApp Earnings Preview: What to Expect
